Recommended implementation cadence
- Phase 1: foundation and platform setup (#1-#7).
- Phase 2: auth and identity (#8-#20).
- Phase 3: event creation and discovery (#21-#33).
- Phase 4: registrations, notifications, host operations (#34-#44).
- Phase 5: end-to-end hardening and deployment (#45-#48).

Notes for future sessions
- Keep each issue narrowly scoped to one mergeable increment.
- Prefer adding migrations and DTOs before handlers/UI that depend on them.
- Do not couple frontend progress to unfinished backend endpoints; use issue ordering to keep interfaces stable.
